    Ticker Formatting Help

    There is a very small set of available formatters:

    • Hashmark: ##text goes here##
      • Wrap your text in hashmarks to apply special header formatting
    • Underscore: __text goes here__
      • Wrap your text in underscores to italicise it
    • Asterisk: **text goes here**
      • Wrap your text in asterisks to make it bold

    Only the strings listed here are available in the ticker template since the context is regenerated for each team.
